Class EMBLFormatModified

    • EMBLFormat

  • public class EMBLFormatModified
extends EMBLFormat
    Code from biojava 1.7.1 org.biojavax.bio.seq.io.EMBLFormat Fixes a bug with parsing EMBL files where an 'XX' line does not separate an 'FT' line from the rest of the sequence

    aaron

      • writeSequence

        public void writeSequence(Sequence seq,
                 java.lang.String format,
                 Namespace ns)
                   throws java.io.IOException
        As per writeSequence(Sequence, Namespace), except that it also takes a format parameter. This can be any of the formats defined as constants in this class.

        seq - see writeSequence(Sequence, Namespace)
        format - the format to use.
